<style>
  body {
    margin: 5px;
    background: #A6A6A6
  }

  /* Tab Navigation */
  .nav-tabs {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      border: 0;    
  }
  .nav-tabs > li > a {
      background: #DADADA;
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: inset 0 -8px 7px -9px rgba(0,0,0,.4),-2px -2px 5px -2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }
  .nav-tabs > li.active > a,
  .nav-tabs > li.active > a:hover {
      background: #F5F5F5;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0 rgba(0,0,0,.4),-2px -3px 5px -2px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }

  .nav-tabs li {
    width: 25%;
    text-align: center;
  }
  /* Tab Content */
  .tab-pane {
      background: #F5F5F5;
      box-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
      border-radius: 0;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      height: auto;
  }

  .tab-content p {
    text-align: justify;
    margin-left: 27%;
    width: 70%;
  }

  .tab-content img {
    width: 245px;
    margin: 25px 0px 0 15px;
  }
</style>

<div class="container">
  <br><br>    
  <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
    <li class="active">
      <a href="#home" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">
        <h4>Dr. Arbind Kumar </h4><span>Principal</span>
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
    
  <div class="tab-content">
    <div class="tab-pane fade active in" id="home">
      <%= image_tag('principal.jpg', alt:"Logo", align: "left") %>
      <h3 style="line-height:25px; margin-bottom:20px;">FROM THE DESK OF PRINCIPAL</h3>

      <p>In the emerging scenario when the life of our young generation is becoming highly challenging, we provide a nurturing and inclusive learning environment where every student can thrive. Our mission is to inspire and empower our students to become lifelong learners, critical thinkers and compassionate individuals who contribute positively to society. Here, I must assert that it has always been our conscious, concerted, and co-ordinated efforts to make education “value based” and “holistic” with a total focus on character building.</p>
      <p>As the head of institution, I feel privileged to have a family of enlightened members of faculty and very supportive parents. Together we will be successful in our mission in true sense, only if we are able to make our children good human beings.</p>
      <p>SGA, Nagla Lallu is centre of excellence and aims to dedicate itself fully to meet the vision of India by transforming students into highly talented individuals with commitment, unity and patriotism.</p>

      <p>I whole heartedly welcome everyone whoever seeks admission to SGA, Nagla Lallu and wish best of luck to all those who are about to complete their schooling from this school.</p>
     
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
